name: A big straight line
description:
Today's train of thought:

"The prairies are terrible. I'd take mountains any day. How many more days of this? Do I even like cycling? Why are my legs moving so slowly? Am I hungry or is it the wind? Man wind is the worst. Unless it's at your back, but it'll never be at my back. What am I doing here? Is this even real life? I can see the sun and the moon at the same time. The sun light is hitting both at once, I bet that looks cool from space. Why am I biking around this rock? I'm so insignificant. Nothing matters."
